OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure builds across the region
OL,7,Fbringing plenty of dry and sunny
OL,8,Fweather throughout the period.
OL,9,FTemperatures increasing by day and
OL,10,Fnight with some very warm and humid
OL,11,Fconditions developing.
